%p Hi #{@recipient.name}!

%br

%p A bid has been made for order with item #{@order.item}.
%p Details are as follows:

%dl.dl-horizontal
  %dt Bidder
  %dd= @bid.bidder.name

  %dt Company
  %dd= @bid.bidder.company_name

  %dt Bid
  %dd= raw @bid.content

%br

%p
  Visit bid
  = link_to 'here', [:buyer, @bid]
